      "description": "InterBuddy is your all-in-one career companion for seamless job searching, AI-powered interview preparation, and personalized career growth. Designed to bridge gaps between job seekers and career opportunities, our app empowers you to land your dream job, refine interview skills, and navigate your career journey with confidence—anytime, anywhere.\nWhether you’re a student preparing for your first job, a professional seeking a career change, or someone honing interview skills for promotion, InterBuddy offers intuitive features tailored to your job search and career needs:\n\n- AI Mock Interviews: Practice with realistic interview scenarios, get instant constructive feedback on your responses, and refine your performance for behavioral, technical, or case study interviews.\n\n- Job Search & Filtering: Explore thousands of job vacancies from various sources, filter by role, location, contract type, and salary, and find the perfect match for your career goals.\n\n- Career Resources: Access interview tips, resume guidance, and real interview experiences shared by placed candidates to boost your preparation.\n\n- Personalized Experience: Customize your job preferences, set targeted job alerts, and get tailored recommendations based on your profile and career aspirations.\n\n- Secure & Private: We prioritize your privacy with strict data protection, ensuring your personal and career information is safe and confidential.\n\nInterBuddy is more than just a job search app—it’s your personal career coach that turns preparation into success. Whether you’re nervous about interviews, struggling to find the right opportunities, or looking to upskill for your next role, InterBuddy is here to make your career journey smoother and more rewarding.",
